<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="48f20a59-b87a-4478-8e3d-53599119ff11" >

    <p>Ryerson is part of an international network of universities and colleges that are committed to solving real-world problems in new and nimble ways. The Faculty of Arts is an environment infused with creative and entrepreneurial thinking which drives our social innovation. This goal fosters learning, teaching and and research innovations. To support Ryerson’s priority to foster an innovation ecosystem, the Faculty of Arts is committed to&nbsp; supporting our social entrepreneurs.</p>
    





